<eesti>Eesti NSV ameti&uuml;hingute seaduse ja ENSV t&ouml;&ouml;koodeksi paragrahvide kehtetuks tunnistamine </eesti>
<inglise>Repeal of sections of Estonian SSR Trade Unions Act and Estonian SSR Labour Code </inglise>
<eesti>Eesti NSV ameti&uuml;hingute seadus (ENSV Teataja 1989, 40, 623; RT 1992, 35, 462) ja ENSV t&ouml;&ouml;koodeksi (ENSV Teataja 1972, 28, lisa 1; 1973, 53, 464; 1975, 9, 69; 1977, 1, 11; 1978, 30, 367; 1980, 9, 121; 16, 178; 31, 491; 1981, 25, 360; 1982, 38, 574; 1984, 16, 178; 49, 577; 1985, 37, 579; 1986, 11, 143; 19, 251; 27, 387; 1987, 4, 38; 47, 634; 1988, 30, 376; 1990, 6, 93; RT 15, 162; 1991, 16, 221; 1992, 35, 462; 1993, 7, 101; RT I 20, 353; 26, 441; 74, 1054; 1994, 2, 12; 11, 154; 12, 199; 1996, 3, 57; 1999, 60, 616) &sect;-d 235-246 tunnistatakse kehtetuks. </eesti>
<inglise>The Estonian SSR Trade Unions Act (ENSV Teataja 1989, 40, 623; RT 1992, 35, 462) and &sect;&sect; 235-246 of the Estonian SSR Labour Code (ENSV Teataja 1972, 28, Appendix 1; 1973, 53, 464; 1975, 9, 69; 1977, 1, 11; 1978, 30, 367; 1980, 9, 121; 16, 178; 31, 491; 1981, 25, 360; 1982, 38, 574; 1984, 16, 178; 49, 577; 1985, 37, 579; 1986, 11, 143; 19, 251; 27, 387; 1987, 4, 38; 47, 634; 1988, 30, 376; 1990, 6, 93; RT 15, 162; 1991, 16, 221; 1992, 35, 462; 1993, 7, 101; RT I 20, 353; 26, 441; 74, 1054; 1994, 2, 12; 11, 154; 12, 199; 1996, 3, 57; 1999, 60, 616) are repealed. (1) RT = Riigi Teataja = State Gazette </inglise>


